title: Daily Wire Backstage: Biden’s Most Terrifying "Accomplishments"
description:
How bad will Biden’s border disaster have to get before the media takes notice? Will Cuomo pull a Northam and just stay in office until the storm passes? Will the Grammys put Pornhub out of business? Plus, get the inside scoop on the recent Candace Owens / Cardi B Twitter feud - and ensuing lawsuit - from none other than Candace Owens herself.
